OL,3,CMan sentenced after death of 'much
OL,4,Cloved' motorcyclist in collision
OL,6,FA Blackpool man has been sentenced
OL,7,Ffollowing a collision in Knott End-on-
OL,8,FSea which killed "much loved" Ian
OL,9,FJoseph Hall, 73.
OL,11,FHall, known as Joe, was killed when a
OL,12,Fcar, driven by Sola Silas, 40, veered
OL,13,Fonto the wrong side of the road and
OL,14,Fcollided with him on 25 October 2023.
OL,16,FJoe was taken to hospital, where he
OL,17,Fdied five days later from his injuries.
