OL,3,CMan sentenced after death of 'much
OL,4,Cloved' motorcyclist in collision
OL,6,FJoe's wife, Karen, said: "he was a
OL,7,Floving, caring husband who loved life
OL,8,Fand looked forward to every day. He
OL,9,Fwas always looking for our next
OL,10,Fadventure and planning for our future.
OL,11,FI have lost my best friend and soul
OL,12,Fmate.
OL,14,F"Joe did nothing wrong and was doing
OL,15,F20mph through the village when Mr
OL,16,FSilas swerved onto Joe's side of the
OL,17,Froad and caused this catastrophic
OL,18,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
