OL,3,CMan sentenced after death of 'much
OL,4,Cloved' motorcyclist in collision
OL,6,F"Despite this, Mr Silas and his
OL,7,Fdefence team then took 19 months of
OL,8,Fstalling and delays before they
OL,9,Ffinally pleaded guilty, which has been
OL,10,Fa living hell for me and my family and
OL,11,Ffor which I will never forgive them.
OL,12,FEven now he has shown little remorse
OL,13,For given us a reason for his careless
OL,14,Factions."
OL,16,FSilas was arrested at the scene and
OL,17,Foriginally pleaded not guilty to
OL,18,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,19,Fbut changed his plea when he appeared
OL,20,Fagain at Preston Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
