OL,6,FOn Wednesday, 13 August he was given a
OL,7,F30 week prison sentence, suspended for
OL,8,Ftwo years, ordered to do 200 hours
OL,9,Funpaid work, and was banned from
OL,10,Fdriving for 12 months.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Matt Davidson, from
OL,13,FLancashire Police's Serious Collision
OL,14,FInvestigation Unit, said: "Joe went
OL,15,Fout for a ride with the intention of
OL,16,Freturning home to his family.
OL,17,FTragically he never did, through
OL,18,Fabsolutely no fault of his own.
