OL,6,F"While we'll never know why Silas
OL,7,Fdrove onto the wrong side of the road,
OL,8,Fthat action resulted in the death of a
OL,9,Fmuch-loved family man.
OL,11,F"Joe's death should serve as a
OL,12,Freminder to other motorists about the
OL,13,Fimportance of always staying alert
OL,14,Fwhen you are behind the wheel and
OL,15,Fbeing extra vigilant for vulnerable
OL,16,Froad users."
